<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>✨ Cool Products 🛍️</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74ebd5, #9face6);
      color: #222;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .products {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 25px;
      color: #fff;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 1.6em;
      color: #ffe066;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.95em;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #f1f1f1;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: #ff6b6b;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #ff4757;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>✨ Our Fresh Picks 🥗🍇</h1>

    <div class="products">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>🍎 Juicy Apples</h2>
        <p>Crisp, sweet, and full of nutrients. A perfect snack for anytime!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>🥕 Organic Carrots</h2>
        <p>Fresh from the farm, crunchy and tasty. Great for your salads & soups.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>🌿 Power Spinach</h2>
        <p>Rich in iron and vitamins. Perfect for smoothies and healthy meals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/contact" class="btn">📞 Get in Touch</a>

    <footer>
      <p>🌟 Freshness Delivered | © 2025</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
